<section class="py-20 bg-surface-container-lowest" id="tgpcop-faq">
  <div class="max-w-container-max mx-auto px-margin-mobile md:px-margin-desktop">
    
    <div class="text-center mb-16 space-y-4">
      <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-black text-primary tracking-tight">Frequently Asked Questions</h2>
      <p class="text-on-surface-variant text-lg">Got questions? We've got answers. Email: <a href="mailto:contact@tgpcoppharma.shop" class="text-primary font-bold">contact@tgpcoppharma.shop</a></p>
    </div>

    <!-- Scrolling Container -->
    <div class="faq-window relative h-[500px] overflow-hidden rounded-[2rem] border-2 border-primary/5 bg-white shadow-2xl">
      <div class="faq-scrolling-track p-8 grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 animate-scroll-vertical">
        
        <!-- FAQ Block 1 -->
        <div class="faq-card p-8 rounded-2xl bg-primary/5 border border-primary/10 hover:bg-primary/10 transition-colors">
          <h4 class="font-black text-primary text-xl mb-3">1. What is TGPCOP NOTES?</h4>
          <p class="text-on-surface-variant leading-relaxed">TGPCOP NOTES is a platform providing handwritten B.Pharmacy notes, study materials, semester bundles, and exam-focused PDFs for pharmacy students.</p>
        </div>

        <!-- FAQ Block 2 -->
        <div class="faq-card p-8 rounded-2xl bg-primary/5 border border-primary/10 hover:bg-primary/10 transition-colors">
          <h4 class="font-black text-primary text-xl mb-3">2. Handwritten or Typed?</h4>
          <p class="text-on-surface-variant leading-relaxed">All notes are premium handwritten PDF notes designed for easy understanding and exam preparation.</p>
        </div>

        <!-- FAQ Block 3 -->
        <div class="faq-card p-8 rounded-2xl bg-primary/5 border border-primary/10 hover:bg-primary/10 transition-colors">
          <h4 class="font-black text-primary text-xl mb-3">3. How to receive notes?</h4>
          <p class="text-on-surface-variant leading-relaxed">After successful payment, the PDF download link will be sent instantly to your email address.</p>
        </div>

        <!-- FAQ Block 4 -->
        <div class="faq-card p-8 rounded-2xl bg-primary/5 border border-primary/10 hover:bg-primary/10 transition-colors">
          <h4 class="font-black text-primary text-xl mb-3">4. Need an account?</h4>
          <p class="text-on-surface-variant leading-relaxed">No, you only need a valid email address to receive your digital products instantly.</p>
        </div>

        <!-- FAQ Block 5 -->
        <div class="faq-card p-8 rounded-2xl bg-primary/5 border border-primary/10 hover:bg-primary/10 transition-colors">
          <h4 class="font-black text-primary text-xl mb-3">5. Useful for exams?</h4>
          <p class="text-on-surface-variant leading-relaxed">Yes, the notes are exam-focused and specially prepared for B.Pharmacy semester exams and quick revision.</p>
        </div>

        <!-- FAQ Block 6 -->
        <div class="faq-card p-8 rounded-2xl bg-primary/5 border border-primary/10 hover:bg-primary/10 transition-colors">
          <h4 class="font-black text-primary text-xl mb-3">6. Which courses?</h4>
          <p class="text-on-surface-variant leading-relaxed">Currently, B.Pharmacy semester notes, bundles, and pharmacy study materials are available.</p>
        </div>

        <!-- FAQ Block 7 -->
        <div class="faq-card p-8 rounded-2xl bg-primary/5 border border-primary/10 hover:bg-primary/10 transition-colors">
          <h4 class="font-black text-primary text-xl mb-3">7. Mobile Access?</h4>
          <p class="text-on-surface-variant leading-relaxed">Yes, all PDFs can be accessed on mobile, tablet, laptop, and desktop devices easily.</p>
        </div>

        <!-- FAQ Block 8 -->
        <div class="faq-card p-8 rounded-2xl bg-primary/5 border border-primary/10 hover:bg-primary/10 transition-colors">
          <h4 class="font-black text-primary text-xl mb-3">8. Downloadable?</h4>
          <p class="text-on-surface-variant leading-relaxed">Yes, all products are instant downloadable PDF files available immediately after purchase.</p>
        </div>

        <!-- FAQ Block 9 -->
        <div class="faq-card p-8 rounded-2xl bg-primary/5 border border-primary/10 hover:bg-primary/10 transition-colors">
          <h4 class="font-black text-primary text-xl mb-3">9. Lifetime Access?</h4>
          <p class="text-on-surface-variant leading-relaxed">Yes, once purchased, you can download and keep the notes permanently on your device.</p>
        </div>

        <!-- FAQ Block 10 -->
        <div class="faq-card p-8 rounded-2xl bg-primary/5 border border-primary/10 hover:bg-primary/10 transition-colors">
          <h4 class="font-black text-primary text-xl mb-3">10. Semester bundles?</h4>
          <p class="text-on-surface-variant leading-relaxed">Yes, complete semester bundles with all subjects are available at discounted prices.</p>
        </div>

        <!-- FAQ Block 11 -->
        <div class="faq-card p-8 rounded-2xl bg-primary/5 border border-primary/10 hover:bg-primary/10 transition-colors">
          <h4 class="font-black text-primary text-xl mb-3">11. Can I share?</h4>
          <p class="text-on-surface-variant leading-relaxed">No, purchased notes are for personal educational use only. Distribution is prohibited.</p>
        </div>

        <!-- FAQ Block 12 -->
        <div class="faq-card p-8 rounded-2xl bg-primary/5 border border-primary/10 hover:bg-primary/10 transition-colors">
          <h4 class="font-black text-primary text-xl mb-3">12. Payment methods?</h4>
          <p class="text-on-surface-variant leading-relaxed">We accept UPI, Debit Card, Credit Card, Net Banking, and all major secure methods.</p>
        </div>

        <!-- FAQ Block 13 -->
        <div class="faq-card p-8 rounded-2xl bg-primary/5 border border-primary/10 hover:bg-primary/10 transition-colors">
          <h4 class="font-black text-primary text-xl mb-3">13. Issue with link?</h4>
          <p class="text-on-surface-variant leading-relaxed">Contact us through WhatsApp, Telegram, or email support and we’ll help you quickly.</p>
        </div>

        <!-- FAQ Block 14 -->
        <div class="faq-card p-8 rounded-2xl bg-primary/5 border border-primary/10 hover:bg-primary/10 transition-colors">
          <h4 class="font-black text-primary text-xl mb-3">14. Updates available?</h4>
          <p class="text-on-surface-variant leading-relaxed">Yes, join our WhatsApp and Telegram channels for regular updates and new uploads.</p>
        </div>

        <!-- FAQ Block 15 -->
        <div class="faq-card p-8 rounded-2xl bg-primary/5 border border-primary/10 hover:bg-primary/10 transition-colors">
          <h4 class="font-black text-primary text-xl mb-3">15. How to contact?</h4>
          <p class="text-on-surface-variant leading-relaxed">You can contact us through WhatsApp, Telegram, Instagram, or email support anytime.</p>
        </div>

      </div>

      <!-- Overlays for smooth fade -->
      <div class="absolute top-0 w-full h-32 bg-gradient-to-b from-white via-white/80 to-transparent z-10 pointer-events-none"></div>
      <div class="absolute bottom-0 w-full h-32 bg-gradient-to-t from-white via-white/80 to-transparent z-10 pointer-events-none"></div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  @keyframes scroll-vertical {
    0% { transform: translateY(0); }
    100% { transform: translateY(-70%); }
  }
  .animate-scroll-vertical {
    animation: scroll-vertical 40s linear infinite;
  }
  .faq-window:hover .animate-scroll-vertical {
    animation-play-state: paused;
  }
</style>

